theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0, 1, 0, 1)
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("2_a2gr8")
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "You are Awake.

The Night has come to an end.

Our triumph shall be like the Jubilation of the heavens.

Our victory shall echo through the cosmos as all of your kind bears witness to their destruction.


We have collapsed the sun.

Meridia is now beset by eternal night, ever sleepless, ever dreaming.

Your labours to prevent us have been futile.


Earth, and all her people will perish.

We are glad you are awake to witness it.
"

